name: HoleFall
description:
This is for brackeys game jam with theme holes. I had only 4days time making this and i really stucked with random generation so game ended up lacking some features. I still hope u can enjoy it. Its really simple but still hard. Just dont shoot too near objectives btw because it can break stuff lol. And yeah if u are true pro try to get 1000points and if u wanna know my personal best is 1600 so even that is possible.

Send ofcourse screenshot of ur record.
